      "span_text": "With these TCGA data on HNSCC we thus established a relation of high intra-tumor heterogeneity to worse outcome in a large, multi-institutional study, for the first time to our knowledge in any type of cancer.  We validated both the overall relation of MATH to HNSCC outcome and a particularly strong relation among patients who received chemoradiation."
